{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"28":{"eng-name":"Chapters on Hunting","ara-name":"كتاب الصيد"}},"section_detail":{"28":{"hadithnumber_first":3200,"hadithnumber_last":3250,"arabicnumber_first":3200,"arabicnumber_last":3250}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":3228,"arabicnumber":3228,"text":"حَدَّثَنَا أَبُو بَكْرِ بْنُ أَبِي شَيْبَةَ، حَدَّثَنَا سُفْيَانُ بْنُ عُيَيْنَةَ، عَنْ عَبْدِ الْحَمِيدِ بْنِ جُبَيْرٍ، عَنْ سَعِيدِ بْنِ الْمُسَيَّبِ، عَنْ أُمِّ شَرِيكٍ، أَنَّ النَّبِيَّ ـ صلى الله عليه وسلم ـ أَمَرَهَا بِقَتْلِ الأَوْزَاغِ ‏.‏","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih - Agreed Upon"}],"reference":{"book":28,"hadith":29},"chapter":{"id":12,"ara-name":"باب قَتْلِ الْوَزَغِ","eng-name":"Killing house lizards","isFirstHadith":true}}]}